    "In addition, entities called healthcare data gateways were used in the data management layer of the proposed scheme.In the study of [18], medical institutions such as hospitals were held responsible for the execution and verification of smart contracts.",
    "In addition, the patient data were kept in different databases in the hospitals.",
    "Thus, in case of attacks on the system from both inside and outside the hospitals, the data could be destroyed.",
    "When the data are kept separately in many databases, it creates a disadvantage in terms of integrity and make data management difficult.In study [14], data were kept in distributed nodes.",
    "A blockchain was used to establish connections on nodes."
  ],
